$

= Inequality

$ x &> x_r
\ v t_x &> x_r
\ a t_c t_x &> x_r
\ a t_c (t - t_c) &> x_r
\ - a t_c^2 + a t t_c &> x_r
\ t_c^2 - t t_c + x_r / a &< 0
$

The roots of the quadratic equation are:
$ t_c = (t plus.minus sqrt(t^2 - 4 x_r / a)) / 2
$

The solution of the inequality is:
$ t_c in lr(\] (t - sqrt(t^2 - 4 x_r / a)) / 2, (t + sqrt(t^2 - 4 x_r / a)) / 2 \[)
$
